Member Enumeration Documentation

enum GTraversal::LoadMode

Enumeration values:
DONT_LOAD   don´t load.
LOAD_FIRST   load first than stop.
LOAD_IF_NEEDED   lazy, load only if needed.
LOAD_ALL   load all.
